Arispe, Press on MILA Equity, Fixed-Income Investing

-- B y  
-- 
2011-09-22T18:21:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/arispe-press-on-mila-equity-fixed-income-investing-video.html
Erich Arispe, head sovereign 
analyst at Fitch Ratings and Jason Press, an analyst at 
Citigroup, participate in a panel discussion about opportunities
for both equity and fixed-income investors on the Mercado 
Integrado Latino Americano(MILA).  They speak at Bloomberg Link's MILA Conference in New York.
Bloomberg's James Crombie moderates the discussion. (Source: 
Bloomberg)  Running time 25:09
 